_Comment.WorldCooldown: Cooldown if cow milked in world (not in stall, like mechanisms)
_Comment.StallCooldown: Cooldown if cow milked from Stall
_Comment.BreedingCooldown: How many ticks it takes before the cow can breed again
_Comment.GrowingAge: How many ticks it takes for the baby cow to grow up
_Comment.Parent First: First parent to fluid (empty is disable) example usage: "lava" "water"
_Comment.Parent Second: Second parent to fluid (empty is disable) example usage: "lava" "water"
_Comment.Tip#1: Cow rewards? Yes! Set enable to true, rate to zero, remove parents and make recipe with CraftTweaker!
_Comment.Tip#2: Only breeding cow? Yes! Set enable to true, rate to zero and add parents!

_Comment Client.HideFluidLayerCow: Disable fluid render layer cow in stall

_Comment General.BreedingItemWork: If true u can use the breeding item to get lower baby growing age
_Comment General.ProjectETickRemove: If true - "Watch of Flowing Time" not work on Cow Stall. From mod "ProjectE"
_Comment General.NotEnoughtWandsTickRemove: If true - "Acceleration Wand" not work on Cow Stall. From mod "Not Enough Wand"
_Comment General.TorcherinoTickRemove: If true - all types "Torcherino" not work on Cow Stall. From mod "Torcherino"
_Comment General.randomthingsTickRemove: If true - "Time in a bottle" not work on Cow Stall. From mod "Random Things"
_Comment General.DisableBreedingItemForMachines: Disables get breeding item via machines
_Comment General.FluidCowsSpawnBlackListBiomes: Fluid cows spawn black list biomes (modid:name)
_Comment General.AcceleratorMaxSubstance: Accelerator max substance per one wheat
_Comment General.AcceleratorSubstancePerCow: Accelerator one substance per one cow
_Comment General.AcceleratorWaterPerConvert: Accelerator water per one substance convert
_Comment General.BlackListDimIds: In what dim Id cow not spawn
_Comment General.EnableConvertCowToDisplayer: If true u can convert cow into displayer via halter
_Comment General.BlackListCowToDisplayer: Black list for 'cow to displayer' convert
_Comment General.FeederBlackList: Black list for 'what cows cant feed with Feeder'
_Comment General.EIOBlackListSpawning: EIO Powered Spawner cant spawn any cow
_Comment General.EIOBlackListSoulVial: EIO Soul Vial cant store any cow
_Comment General.EIONeedsCloning: EIO Powered Spawner cloning cow every time (prevents spawn random cows from spawner)
_Comment General.EIOEntityCostMultiplier: EIO Powered Spawner need multiplier energy cost to spawn cow
